---
title: Glazed Halloumi Loaded Patatas Bravas with Garlic Aioli and Rocket
description: A Spanish favourite, bravas sauce is lightly spiced with paprika before it's spooned over roasted potatoes to make patatas bravas. Here, we're making a quick garlic aioli and topping with glazed halloumi for a hearty vegetarian dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R47_W44_UK_HVV26336-3_Main__4low-a0e4d21f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66cd8cee6041110ff0a4be44-en-GB.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/glazed-halloumi-loaded-patatas-bravas-66cd8cee6041110ff0a4be44
